            <title>[PIG-882] log level not propogated to loggers </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-882</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Pig accepts log level as a parameter. But the log level it captures is not set appropriately, so that loggers in different classes log at the specified level.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
